hscan                                 macro                                hscan

NAME
     hhssccaann - scan along the HH-axis in reciprocal space

SYNOPSIS

     hhssccaann ssttaarrtt eenndd iinntteerrvvaallss ttiimmee

DESCRIPTION

     hhssccaann is a linear scan in reciprocal space along the HH-axis from ssttaarrtt to
     eenndd. The step size is ((ssttaarrtt--eenndd))//iinntteerrvvaallss.  The number of data points
     collected will be iinntteerrvvaallss++11.  Count time is given by ttiimmee, which if
     positive, specifies seconds and if negative, specifies monitor counts.

EXAMPLE

     hhssccaann ..99 11..11 1100 1100

